org.osate.xtext.aadl2.errormodel.errorModel

Interface ErrorPath

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AObject, Element, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, ErrorFlow, org.eclipse.core.runtime.IAdaptable, NamedElement, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ErrorPathImpl

    public interface ErrorPath
extends ErrorFlow
    A representation of the model object 'Error Path'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Incoming
    • Outgoing
    • All
    • Target Token
    • Type Mapping Set

    See Also:
    ErrorModelPackage.getErrorPath()
